Class EmployeeChart

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.khalsa_ji.ems.EmployeeChart

  • public class EmployeeChart
extends java.lang.Object
    The EmployeeChart class defines various properties of a typical employee information system/dashboard along with methods to play around with those properties.
